cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CE, cs.DS, cs.FL 

This paper involves the use of a feed forward neural network (FFNN) and memory structure to improve investment decision making. This suggests that it is likely to fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE). Additionally, the use of memory recall and contextual similarity assessment suggests that it may also fall under the categories of data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.FL).
